I"å<p>In <strong>_layout.scss</strong> file, &lt; q &gt; tag is used as a quotation mark. When apply this tag, it will display as â€œã€ã€â€ on the page. One user report that on Windows it may cause a Error â€œinvalid CPC949 characterâ€ when generate the site. A fast way to avoid this problem, please delete the lines of &lt; q &gt; tags in the <strong>_layout.scss</strong> file.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>### DELETE THE CODE BELOW IN _layout.scss FILE###
